  "text": "Cytotoxicity of extracts was evaluated by MTT assay. Cells were treated for 48 h with different extracts of B. aegyptiaca or 1 % DMSO as a negative control. Viability of cells was determined by MTT test as described previously [CITATION_1] . Assay plates were read using a microplate reader (Tecan infinite bro 2000) at absorbance 570. The results are presented as percentage inhibition to the negative control (n = 3).",
